briefDescription: AL HIND YOUVA SANGH (AHYS) social development and welfare society is a non-Profit voluntary organization engaged in social development services was registered on August 8, 2003 under the society registration act-xxi of 1860, by group of professionals who shared the common dream and had some together to work on a people-centric  model of development in area, like public health education gender child welfare community development and social welfare and skill programme.
